        -- Posted by LallanKamormson on 2:49 pm on June 8, 2001<p>
        In case you didnt know, the range slot is very advantageous all classes. &nbsp;no just people that use range attacks. &nbsp;For those caster or hybrid classes that dont use a bow, shuriken or throwing knives. <br> <br>certain in game items can be placed there. &nbsp;if the item has ac or some stat modifiers, you get them. &nbsp; <br> <br>couple good examples shaman and harpoons or spears <br> <br>sarnak ceremonial daggers for druids. <br> <br>ball pein hammer i found in warrens once with &nbsp;my druid, put it on warrior and it gives 2 str 2 dex 6 ac. &nbsp;might not seem like much, but every little bit helps.

        <p><p>
        
